title: [Shattered Moors, Salt Marsh]
description: Tall cattails and reeds crowd each other.  Cordgrass grows thickly in rich diluvial soil deposited by the brackish water.  A high-pitched hum draws attention to a cloud of moquitoes hovering over the winding path.  The cool light of the moons casts a strange silvery hue on the path.

Tall cattails and reeds crowd each other.  Cordgrass grows thickly in rich diluvial soil deposited by the brackish water.  A high-pitched hum draws attention to a cloud of moquitoes hovering over the winding path.  The heat of the sun cannot lessen the stickiness of the still air.
